<view wx:if="{{visible}}" class="modal-mask" catchtap="noop">
  <view class="modal" catchtap="noop">
    <view class="modal-title">设置开始前提醒</view>
    <view class="modal-sub">预约时间：{{booking.date}} {{booking.timeLabel || booking.startTime}}</view>
    <view class="modal-sub" wx:if="{{booking.venueName}}">场室：{{booking.venueName}}</view>

    <view wx:if="{{tooLate}}" class="tip-box">
      当前预约时间较近，已无法设置“开始前再次提醒”。您仍可保留预约成功通知。
    </view>

    <block wx:else>
      <view class="tip-box">请选择希望在开始前多久再次提醒。</view>
      <picker-view class="pv" indicator-style="height: 44px;" value="{{pickerValue}}" bindchange="onPickerChange">
        <picker-view-column>
          <view wx:for="{{hourOptions}}" wx:key="value" class="pv-item">{{item.label}}</view>
        </picker-view-column>
        <picker-view-column>
          <view wx:for="{{minuteOptions}}" wx:key="value" class="pv-item">{{item.label}}</view>
        </picker-view-column>
      </picker-view>
      <view class="summary-box">
        <view class="summary-title">提醒设置</view>
        <view class="summary-text">开始前 {{leadText}} 提醒</view>
        <view class="summary-text">预计发送时间：{{reminderAtText}}</view>
      </view>
    </block>

    <view class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" bindtap="onSkip">暂不设置</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="onConfirm">确定</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
